cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.MM

The paper proposes a method for detecting red lesions in fundus images using a combination of deep learning and domain knowledge. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. Additionally, the use of hand-crafted features and a random forest classifier suggests that the paper may also be relevant to the artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and information retrieval (cs.IR) sub-categories. Finally, the use of fundus images suggests that the paper may also be relevant to the multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category.
